Organization Name: AGING AND DISABILITY RESOURCE CENTER (ADRC) OF TARRANT COUNTY | AGING DISABILITY RESOURCE CENTER OF TARRANT COUNTY | HOUSING NAVIGATION
Description:
Provides resources on housing options, local resources for unhoused, fair housing education, and information regarding accessible, integrated, and affordable housing. Assists with completing applications only.
Note: The agency is not associated with any Housing Authority. Housing Navigation does not provide housing placement. Limited housing case management provided.
